01:08:40.390 --> 01:08:42.230 position:56%
You're giving a talk here next week,

01:08:42.230 --> 01:08:45.360
what will the subject
of that lecture be?

01:08:45.360 --> 01:08:50.400
&gt;&gt; Ingrid Monson: It
is called "Miles Davis

01:08:50.400 --> 01:08:53.590
and John Coltrane as
Living Ancestors."

01:08:53.590 --> 01:08:55.280
And I'm going to talk
about relationship

01:08:55.280 --> 01:08:57.790
to African stuff in there.

01:08:57.790 --> 01:09:00.250
&gt;&gt; Larry Appelbaum: So
that will be next Thursday?

01:09:00.250 --> 01:09:01.550
&gt;&gt; Ingrid Monson: Yes.

